A '''gestor''' or '''gestoría''' is person who, in [[Spain]] or [[Mexico]], deals with administrative bureaucracy on behalf of a client. In Spain they need not be a licensed [[lawyer|attorney]].<ref name=Gestor>{{cite web|title=The Gestor / Gestoria|url=http://www.spainexpat.com/spain/information/the_gestor_gestoria/|publisher=SpainExpat.com|accessdate=April 22, 2012|author="algrif"|date=July 3, 2008}}</ref> In Spain, Gestors are listed in the ''[[Yellow Pages|Páginas Amarillas]]'' (the yellow pages) as "gestorias".<ref>[http://www.paginasamarillas.es/gestorias/all-ma/all-pr/all-is/all-ci/all-ba/all-pu/all-nc/1 Yellow pages listing Spain]</ref>
